c: 6
v: 91
t: "They do not make the right measure of the Power of Allah when they say: \"Allah sends nothing down to man (as revelation):\" Say: \"Who then sent down the Book (Torah) that Musa (Moses) brought? (It is) a light and a guidance to man: But you make it into (separate) sheets for show, while you hide much (of its contents): In there, you were taught that which you did not know— Neither you nor your fathers.\" Say: \"Allah (sent it down):\" Then leave them to sink into idle talk and meaningless remarks"